{"tid":1242470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［撐警隊 反暴力］估下今次又幾多人","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:23:10.000Z","uid":264234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"237863ed9ecba25f284e21dc801c256f2095a23d","tid":1242470,"uid":264234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wB9xV2R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwB9xV2R.png&h=14ffd460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n難用正邪定分界的香港<br />\n天雖是藍的 <br />\n你可明白大家的心已變灰了 <br />\n<br />\n努力興建，盡情破壞的紛亂下，為公義，為公道，為公理，作為紀律部隊成員的我們要團結一致，皆因今天的反響讓我們看到將來的路 ...只會更難行，今天站出來相互支持，為紀律部隊成員送上一分認同，懇請大家，6月30日當天撥出三個小時，帶同所有支持我們的友好！為紀律部隊成員站起來吧！<br />\n<br />\n約定您：<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n6月30日 週日<br />\n下午3至6時"},{"pid":"29b619bccf030964a8f82f1871157170f87adfb6","tid":1242470,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffc574a76edf226d2a94862643dfd7b3179de4c","tid":1242470,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"瞓咗冇睇 上次有幾多人？"},{"pid":"80853d636ec22df98b703e92bd6611b9c323522e","tid":1242470,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"撐警隊 反暴力<br />\n咁矛盾既"},{"pid":"a87ba305fb30bfedc11a1a0867473000e061cce5","tid":1242470,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}